race.comment: Wide open with plenty of win chances. VERY FAMOUS (12) was well in the market on debut but slow to begin and always well back before finishing only a couple of lengths from the winner. Can only be improved and worth following up. AREAAN (1) returns from a good break and has some good figures behind her especially fresh. Drawn well and among the chances. CINCINCITY (5) also resumes after a long break. Was overdue last time in and returns from a tricky gate but has the form to get off the mark here. SOMERSAULT (15) eased back and got home late over 1000m on debut and looks suited by the extra ground this time.
